com.cyc.baseclient.subl

Interface SubLGlobalVariable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The variable's value type
    All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Object>, CycObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicSubLGlobalVariable

    public interface SubLGlobalVariable<T>
extends CycObject
    A Java representation of a SubL global variable.

    Note that this interface does not currently define a method for evaluating the variable. Because there can be a lot of variability to return types, this is left to the implementation. However, classes may be added which will extend com.cyc.baseclient.subl.generaltypes.BasicSubLVariable to provide evaluation methods.
